{"type":"message","id":"7b022f8d","parentId":"c6c2b82a","timestamp":"2026-03-22T06:43:17.362Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Zach said he had an eye exam a few months ago. I should ask if he mentioned the floaters/smoke symptoms then, and if not, whether he should go back. This could be new symptoms developing.","thinkingSignature":"8294f434cdf0ed0f5e9b8a03fdef3c56e1ca8b6a7a7bdbfc97ce21576aab1cf4"},{"type":"text","text":"Did you mention the floaters/smoke stuff at that exam? If not, definitely bring it up — even if it turns out to be nothing, you want it documented if it changes."}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":43,"output":88,"cacheRead":15661,"cacheWrite":264,"totalTokens":16056,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1774161792483}}
