{"type":"message","id":"13a1fd87","parentId":"abe40320","timestamp":"2026-03-22T06:51:07.691Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_gm21jt8x6u9f_1","toolName":"exec","content":[{"type":"text","text":"neu: \nEXP: \nattention: \nhgsel-moe: \ntinymen: \ntemporal-attention: Temporal + Attention memory system for AI\ninfant: \nselfhelper: \ngpume: \ngrid-chat-new: User-friendly AI Interface (Supports Ollama, OpenAI API, ...)\nschemocker: JSON Schema → live mock REST API in 60 seconds. Single-binary mock server for frontend teams building React/Next/Vue UIs before backends exist. Zero dependencies, works offline, perfect for prototyping & Cypress/Playwright testing.\ncircuit_lm: \naipg-art-gallery: \nsmollm3_finetune: \ncomfy-bridge: A python bridge to turn your ComfyUI instance into a grid worker.\n123: \nparticleblood-rust-gpu: Rust/WebGL2 GPU particle sim variant of particleblood\nAutoBrand: \nzach: \ncolabb: \nselhelpbot: \ntime: \nARC-AGI: The Abstraction and Reasoning Corpus\ngraph_ir: \nsurtool: \ncollab: \ncontextual-flux: \nmind: \nsep-w: \ncontext:"}],"details":{"status":"completed","exitCode":0,"durationMs":1624,"aggregated":"neu: \nEXP: \nattention: \nhgsel-moe: \ntinymen: \ntemporal-attention: Temporal + Attention memory system for AI\ninfant: \nselfhelper: \ngpume: \ngrid-chat-new: User-friendly AI Interface (Supports Ollama, OpenAI API, ...)\nschemocker: JSON Schema → live mock REST API in 60 seconds. Single-binary mock server for frontend teams building React/Next/Vue UIs before backends exist. Zero dependencies, works offline, perfect for prototyping & Cypress/Playwright testing.\ncircuit_lm: \naipg-art-gallery: \nsmollm3_finetune: \ncomfy-bridge: A python bridge to turn your ComfyUI instance into a grid worker.\n123: \nparticleblood-rust-gpu: Rust/WebGL2 GPU particle sim variant of particleblood\nAutoBrand: \nzach: \ncolabb: \nselhelpbot: \ntime: \nARC-AGI: The Abstraction and Reasoning Corpus\ngraph_ir: \nsurtool: \ncollab: \nconte