{"type":"message","id":"5239204a","parentId":"4a272ed8","timestamp":"2026-03-22T07:56:54.013Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Now I'll add the WorldState integration. The key places to modify:\n1. Add import for WorldState/detectFk\n2. Modify `handleGetById` to resolve FKs on generated entities\n3. Modify `handleGetCollection` to resolve FKs\n4. Modify `handlePost` to resolve FKs on new items\n5. Modify `handlePut` to resolve FKs on updated items\n\nThe pattern: after creating/generating an entity object, call `resolveEntity` from WorldState (stored on state._world).\n\nFor ServerState type - it's `Record<string, JSONValue[]>`. I can't add arbitrary properties to it... or can I? TypeScript's type system says `Record<string, JSONValue[]>` but at runtime it's just an object so I can add `_world`.\n \nTypeScript will complain about accessing `_world` on ServerState since it only expects string arrays, but I'll use type casting to work around that. Actually, I think the cleaner approach is to initialize WorldState lazily inside the handler closures themselves, keeping it scoped locally rather than trying to store it on the state object. to existing code\n\nLet me go with a cleaner approach - modify `createRouteHandler` to accept an optional `WorldState` instance, and create a new version `createRouteHandlerWithWorld` that wraps the handlers.\n\nActually, the simplest approach that doesn't change any existing interfaces:\n\n1. Create the WorldState lazily in `createRouteHandler`'s closure scope\n2. Expose it via `state._world` (TypeScript will complain, use `as any`)\n3. Initialize on first use in any handler\n\nLet me write the integration now. I'll add a helper `resolveWithWorld` that takes entity data, resolves FKs, and registers with WorldState.\n\nHere's the key integration - modifying `createRouteHandler` to create and use WorldState:","thinkingSignature":"59ad184fc3cf2f5d008a53fcfd3910c38070ba57eb67a9acde93ab1ad877f2a8"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_ai4bv16riqfy_1","name":"read","arguments":{"path":"C:\\Users\\Zwmar\\dev\\schemock-app\\src\\generators\\schema-routes.ts","offset":270,"limit":20}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":54731,"output":452,"cacheRead":12454,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":67637,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1774166201191}}
