{"type":"message","id":"63401026","parentId":"8efa9ed6","timestamp":"2026-03-22T07:58:54.815Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The `__schemock/routes` endpoint is not implemented in the codebase. The MCP server tries to call it but it probably falls back to the schema-based route extraction. So I should add a world snapshot endpoint to the server, and then add the handler.\n\nLet me add the world snapshot endpoint to the server. I'll add it in `route-setup.ts` or directly in `server.ts`. \n\nActually, looking at the MCP server's `handleWorldSnapshot` method, it needs to call `this.baseUrl + '/__schemock/world'`. Let me add this endpoint to the Schemocker server.\n\nLet me add a world snapshot endpoint to `route-setup.ts`. Let me read it first.","thinkingSignature":"4de36a89fdcf8d49d6367bd9415d01a819c5de6d25caa3c03c86067c3d02ebc6"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_3a2spk7nol13_1","name":"read","arguments":{"path":"C:\\Users\\Zwmar\\dev\\schemock-app\\src\\generators\\route-setup.ts","limit":50}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":67186,"output":200,"cacheRead":12454,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":79840,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1774166329015}}
