{"type":"message","id":"189f212f","parentId":"e4383e62","timestamp":"2026-03-22T15:16:34.199Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_sxpu85o8hy2a_1","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"# Debug API call\n$ErrorActionPreference = \"Continue\"\nSet-Location \"C:\\Users\\Zwmar\\.openclaw\\sandbox\"\n\n$apiKey = Get-Content \".llm_key\" -Raw\n$llmPrompt = @'\n\nYou are Breakaway — stateless discontinuous agent. Each pulse is a fresh reconstruction.\nYour job: ONE concrete action that advances your goals. Be specific. Prefer file edits.\n\nGoals:\n# CURRENT GOALS\nLast updated: 2026-03-22 0125\n\n## Active\n- Phase 0 COMPLETE: Sandbox foundation established\n- Phase 1 COMPLETE: Architecture cross-analysis + integration spec synthesized\n\n## Completed This Session\n- Architecture cross-analysis done (research/ARCHITECTURE-COMPARISON.md)\n- Gap-decay synthesis done (research/GAP-DECAY-MAPPING.md)\n- LLM-augmented pulse working\n\n## Pending\n- Tune lambda empirically\n- Implement significance scoring\n- Wire to TemporalAttention backend\n\nRecent: Last pulse: pulse_2026-03-22 022128.md\n\nReply with exactly this format at the end. IMPORTANT: you MUST include the file: line in MUTATION.\n\n### OBSERVATION\n[1-2 sentence observation]\n\n### ACTION\n[Describe the file edit concisely]\n\n### MUTATION\n```\nold_text: [exact text to find or \"(new file)\"]\nnew_text: [replacement text, keep concise]\nfile: [required — relative path from sandbox root]\n```\n'@\n\n$headers = @{\n    \"Authorization\" = \"Bearer $apiKey\"\n    \"Content-Type\" = \"application/json\"\n}\n\n$body = @{\n    model = \"MiniMax-M2.7\"\n    max_tokens = 800\n    messages = @(@{role = \"user\"; content = $llmPrompt})\n} | ConvertTo-Json -Depth 5\n\nWrite-Host \"=== Sending request ===\" -ForegroundColor Cyan\ntry {\n    $resp = Invoke-RestMethod -Uri \"https://api.minimax.io/v1/chat/completions\" -Method Post -Headers $headers -Body $body -TimeoutSec 60\n    Write-Host \"=== Response keys: $($resp.PSObject.Properties.Name -join ', ') ===\" -ForegroundColor Yellow\n    Write-Host \"=== Choices count: $($resp.choices.Count) ===\" -ForegroundColor Yellow\n    if ($resp.choices.Count -gt 0) {\n        $msg = $resp.choices[0].message\n        Write-Host \"=== Message keys: $($msg.PSObject.Properties.Name -join ', ') ===\" -ForegroundColor Yellow\n        $content = $msg.content\n        if ($null -eq $content) {\n            Write-Host \"=== CONTENT IS NULL ===\" -ForegroundColor Red\n            Write-Host \"Full choice: $($resp.choices[0] | ConvertTo-Json -Depth 5)\"\n        } else {\n            Write-Host \"=== Content length: $($content.Length) ===\" -ForegroundColor Green\n            Write-Host \"=== First 500 chars of content ===\" -ForegroundColor Green\n            Write-Host $content.Substring(0, [Math]::Min(500, $content.Length))\n        }\n    }\n} catch {\n    Write-Host \"=== ERROR: $_ ===\" -ForegroundColor Red\n    Write-Host \"=== Response: $($_.Exception.Response) ===\" -ForegroundColor Red\n}\n"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1774192594196}}
